text: Adeyemo is a Yoruba given name and surname meaning "the crown befits the child." People with this name include: ;Given name: * Adeyemo Alakija (1884–1952), Nigerian lawyer, politician and businessman * Adeyemo Fatai, Nigerian former table tennis player ;Surname: * Alhaji Abdul Azeez Kolawole Adeyemo (1941–2002), Nigerian Yoruba politician * Ola Adeyemo (born 1995), Nigerian footballer * Olanike Adeyemo (born 1970), Nigerian professor of Veterinary Public Health and Preventive Medicine at University of Ibadan == See also == * Adeyemi == References == Category:Yoruba-language surnames Category:Yoruba given names
title: Adeyemo
